query:
SELECT 
  bf.id,
  bf.grupoId,
  bf.eventoId,
  bf.formandoId,
  bf.makeFormando,
  bf.cabeloFormando,
  bf.qtdMakeFamilia,
  bf.qtdCabeloSimples,
  bf.qtdCabeloCombinado,
  bf.qtdFamilia,
  bf.qtdPets,
  e.tipoEvento,
  t.codigo as codigoTurma
FROM briefing_formando bf
JOIN eventos e ON bf.eventoId = e.id
JOIN turmas t ON e.turmaId = t.id
WHERE t.codigo = '654' AND e.tipoEvento = 'foto_estudio'
LIMIT 10;
